Class PullReplication

java.lang.Object
  com.cloudant.sync.replication.Replication
      com.cloudant.sync.replication.PullReplication

public class PullReplication
extends Replication

Provides configuration for a pull replication.

A pull replication is from a remote Cloudant or CouchDB database to the device's local datastore.
